introduction.step1:
Introduction


FPT.AI Console is an integrated management platform for developers to build, manage and get insights into every service that you use for your projects and applications.

FPT.AI Console allows you to:
-    Create a Project
-    Enable an API in the Project
-    Get full user guide and documentation (credentials, parameters…)
-    Manage API’s usage
-    Choose an appropriate package as per demand

Let’s get started!
introduction.step2:
Introduction


This tutorial covers the core features of Fpt.ai Console to get you ready to use apis, services on FPT.AI Platform.

You'll learn about the following concepts:

  • Apis & Services

  • Technical support

Let's get started!
